sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway/Envoy Proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant BBR as Body Based Router<br/>9004/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant ModelPod as Model Server Pod<br/>(vLLM/SGLang/Triton)
    participant LatencyPred as Latency Prediction<br/>8001+/TCP HTTP
    participant OTel as OTel Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 1: Inference Request Processing (with BBR)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9004, TLS
    BBR->>BBR: Parse body, extract "model" field
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Lookup ConfigMap (LoRA→base model)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>BBR: ConfigMap data
    BBR-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>+ X-Gateway-Model-Name header

    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9002, TLS
    Note over EPP: Scheduling Pipeline:<br/>1. Filter (prefix-cache, SLO headroom)<br/>2. Score (queue, kv-cache, prefix-cache)<br/>3. Pick (weighted random)

    opt Latency Prediction Enabled
        EPP->>LatencyPred: GET /predict?...<br/>HTTP/8001+
        LatencyPred-->>EPP: Predicted TTFT/TPOT
    end

    EPP->>ModelPod: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP (configurable)
    ModelPod-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics<br/>(KV cache, queue, running requests)
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>+ selected endpoint address
    Gateway->>ModelPod: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/8000 (cluster internal)
    ModelPod-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    opt Tracing Enabled
        EPP->>OTel: Export spans<br/>gRPC/4317
    end

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 2: Model Name Extraction (BBR standalone)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9004, TLS
    BBR->>BBR: Extract "model" from JSON body
    BBR-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>+ X-Gateway-Model-Name: llama-3-70b

    Note over EPP,ModelPod: Flow 3: Continuous Metrics Collection

    loop Every 50ms (configurable)
        EPP->>ModelPod: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (configurable)
        ModelPod-->>EPP: KV cache utilization,<br/>queue depth, running requests,<br/>LoRA adapter info
    end

    Note over EPP: Prometheus Scraping (every 5s)
    EPP->>EPP: Flush internal metrics<br/>to Prometheus endpoint (9090/TCP)
